NEW Funzione media oraria

hourlyMean <- function(IN.raster, IN.times, sel.times){
  
  stopifnot(nlyr(IN.raster)==length(IN.times))
  
  OUT.raster <- rast(MyGrid)
  OUT.times  <- character() 
   
  for(time in sel.times){
    # print(time)
    
    interval <- format(seq(ymd_hm(time) - hours(1) + minutes(1), 
                           ymd_hm(time), 
                           by="1 min"), "%Y%m%d%H%M")
    
    idx <- which(IN.times %in% interval)
    
    OUT.raster <- c(OUT.raster, mean(IN.raster[[idx]]))
    OUT.times <- c(OUT.times, time)
  }
  
  names(OUT.raster) <- OUT.times
  stopifnot(nlyr(OUT.raster)==length(OUT.times))
  
  return(OUT.raster) 
}
